<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Package Location Update</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; color: #000000;">
<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.95) 0%, rgba(248,249,250,0.98) 100%); padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.2); border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3);">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h1 style="color: #800020; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">Package on the Move!</h1>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">Hi <%= name %>,</p>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">Your package is making progress! Here's the latest location update for your shipment.</p>

    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3); margin: 20px 0; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; color: #800020;">
        Tracking Number: <%= trackingNumber %>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3);">
        <div style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #800020; margin-bottom: 10px;">
            Current Location: <%= location %>
        </div>
        <div style="color: #000000; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            Last Updated: <%= updateTime %>
        </div>

        <% if (estimatedArrival) { %>
            <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 3px solid #c44569; margin-top: 15px;">
                <strong style="color: #000000;">ðŸ•’ Estimated Arrival:</strong> <%= estimatedArrival %>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">Your package is on its way and we'll continue to keep you updated with real-time location information as it moves closer to its destination.</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= trackingUrl %>" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #800020 0%, #a00028 100%); color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3); box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.15); transition: background 0.3s ease;">Track Your Package</a>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Thank you for choosing <%= appName %>. We're committed to keeping you informed every step of the way!</p>

    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #c44569;">
        <strong style="color: #000000;">Questions?</strong><br>
        Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #c44569;"><%= supportEmail %></a> if you need assistance.
    </div>
</div>

<div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center;">
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.<br>
    This email was sent regarding tracking number <%= trackingNumber %>
</div>
</body>
</html>